Package jetbrains.mps.persistence

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataLocationAwareModelFactory
    DataSource is a plain data location, and should not know about snode, smodel, et cetera.
    IndexAwareModelFactory
    PROVISIONAL API Extension to model factory to distinguish model persistence that cares about (usually platform) indexing support and knows how to extract appropriate pieces from actual model persistence state.
    IndexAwareModelFactory.Callback
    Callback implementation shall tolerate duplicated notifications
    LoadedStrategyAware
    Some model implementations may indicate the strategy (= ModelFactory) which was used to load the model from the disk or to create the model.
    MetaModelInfoProvider
    PROVISIONAL API, DO NOT USE
    ModelDigestHelper.DigestProvider  
    ModelRootWalkListener
    Passed to the ModelSourceRootWalker
    PersistenceVersionAware
    PROVISIONAL API Indicator for models that track version of model persistence.
